NAME
    HTTP::Tiny::NewestFirefox - HTTP::Tiny + set User-Agent to newest
    Firefox

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of HTTP::Tiny::NewestFirefox (from
    Perl distribution HTTP-Tiny-NewestFirefox), released on 2019-05-08.

SYNOPSIS
     use HTTP::Tiny::NewestFirefox;

     my $res  = HTTP::Tiny->new->get("http://www.example.com/");

DESCRIPTION
    A convenient bundling of HTTP::Tiny, HTTP::Tiny::Patch::SetUserAgent,
    and HTTP::UserAgentStr::Util::ByNickname.

